name: Mickey Mouse
overview: In this series of cartoon shorts, Mickey Mouse finds himself in silly situations all around the world! From New York to Paris to Tokyo, Mickey experiences new adventures with his friends!

So he tries to work his way around the commute on the train by climbing the hang grips over a sea of punk-rock like teens, working his way through several people in beige coats, and fighting a sumo-wrestler.
